EN: Combing your hair helps with scalp blood circulation.

ZH: 我需要买一把新的梳子。
EN: I need to buy a new comb.

ZH: 梳理头发对于保持头发光滑有很大帮助。
EN: Combing your hair helps keep it smooth.

ZH: 她的发梢看起来非常整齐，一定是梳子梳的。
EN: Her hair looks very neat at the ends, it must have been combed well.
